abstract: Police are investigating whether strong wind gusts played role in death of Clifford LeMay, building manager who fell from roof of Glenpointe office complex in Teaneck, NJ.

headline.print_headline: Fatal Fall Inquiry Focuses on Winds
headline.main: Police Investigating Whether Strong Winds Played Role in Fatal Fall in New Jersey

snippet: Clifford LeMay, 57, went to the roof of an office complex where he works as a building manager to assess damage that may have been caused by strong winds.
lead_paragraph: Clifford LeMay, 57, went to the roof of an office complex where he works as a building manager to assess damage that may have been caused by strong winds.
